Notes:
  - Device Static (85 mW) is the quiescent leakage of the xc7a35tcpg236-1 device.
  - Dynamic power (22 mW) assumes 100 MHz operation with a typical XOR inference
    workload (sparse spikes, ~3 neurons active per timestep on average).
  - Event-driven STDP disabled (SW[3]=0); enabling STDP adds ~2-3 mW.
  - During idle timesteps (no spikes), dynamic power drops to ~5 mW.

